perl-gtk2-gladexml|-----handy-ruler------------------------------------------------------|
perl-gtk2-gladexml: perl-gtk2-gladexml (Create user interfaces from Glade XML files)
perl-gtk2-gladexml:
perl-gtk2-gladexml: Glade is a free user interface builder for GTK+ and GNOME.
perl-gtk2-gladexml: After designing a user interface with glade-2 the layout and
perl-gtk2-gladexml: configuration are saved in an XML file. libglade is a library which
perl-gtk2-gladexml: knows how to build and hook up the user interface described in the
perl-gtk2-gladexml: Glade XML file at application run time.
perl-gtk2-gladexml:
perl-gtk2-gladexml: http://search.cpan.org/dist/Gtk2-GladeXML/
